org.azyva.dragom.model.config

Interface MutableModuleConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModuleConfig, MutableNodeConfig, NodeConfig

    public interface MutableModuleConfig
extends ModuleConfig, MutableNodeConfig
    Extension of ModuleConfig that allows changing the configuration data.

    This interface is an empty extension of MutableNodeConfig since the only configuration data that can be changed for ModuleConfig is that of MutableNodeConfig.

    Author:
    David Raymond

    MutableConfig
